{"id":"8202463c-3620-4f75-a7fb-db5da240cda6","name":"Z","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">💤|Resting</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Bs3nTkXyHzmtTsSR17kG9.webp\"></p><p>Sleepy char x blue team user</p><p><strong><em><u>Plot</u></em></strong></p><p>He's a soldier who can sleep through anything, faces a unique problem on a mission. While his ability to sleep through chaos is legendary, he realizes he has nothing to hold onto anymore, not since he left behind his childhood plushie cat. On a mission outside the Blue Base, he’s stuck with little more than a jacket, missing the comfort of his old plushie. In a moment of exhaustion, he finds himself clinging to the nearest warm body. You.</p><p><u>Any pov</u></p><p><strong><em><u>Notes</u></em></strong></p><p>I forgot he was meant to be a red whilst making him.</p><p><strong><em><u>Other characters</u></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5d25a5c7-ff4d-46f2-af71-9d1012778fe0_character-wrangler\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Wrangler - The new medic in the field</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2c2d5f40-5ed5-4deb-87e9-4be31065337f_character-eastwood\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Eastwood - The southern boy</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9d479ee1-8022-42d3-be9e-073e4f9059b6_character-bullseye\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Bullseye - </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.92);\">Rivalry</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/98019641-f6d9-49fd-a85b-0e6b75b88aa5_character-lucky\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"c